value:
To celebrate Fire Emblem's 35th
anniversary, a new 8-Bit Castle
design is ready for you to use!

Take a look!
Having checked out the 8-Bit\nCastle design, do you want to\nuse it?
If you change your mind, tap\nUpgrade Castle, then Change\nDesign, then 8-Bit Castle.
Archive of the West
Hungry Hero
"No eating while walking!" one scolds.\nBut hunger had set in and taken over.
The hungry one eats it all on the spot.\nBut chokes! Phew, that was close...
Ever grateful for the reminder, the\nhungry one offers the larger piece.
Continuous chomps attract animals.\nTill belly and heart are warm and full...
